Package com.iontrading.mkv.events

Provides Listener and Event interfaces used by the ION Bus Java API.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MkvAuthenticatedLicenseListener
    Interface used for notifying authenticated license events.
    MkvAuthenticateUserRequest
    Interface used for user authentication requests.
    MkvAuthenticateUserRequestListener
    Interface used for notifying OnBehalfOf generic user authentication events.
    MkvAuthenticateUserRequestListener.MkvAuthenticateUserResult  
    MkvAuthenticationListener
    Interface used for notifying authentication events.
    MkvAuthenticationListenerExt
    Interface used for notifying authentication events.
    MkvAvailabilityListener
    Interface used for notifying availability events.
    MkvChainListener
    Interface used for notifying events on chains.
    MkvCheckTokenCompletionListener  
    MkvCustomStatsListener
    This interface defines the handler Custom Applications can use to produce their non-standard statistics on demand, synchronizing with the standard performance indicator reporting to Daemon Master.
    MkvDataSupplyListener Deprecated.
    Provided only for porting purpose.
    MkvEntitlementListEvalListener
    Interface used for notifying responses to list entitlement requests a component has issued.
    MkvEntitlementRequestEvalListener
    Interface used for notifying responses to entitlement requests a component has issued.
    MkvEntitlementRequestEvalListenerExt
    Interface used for notifying responses to entitlement requests a component has issued.
    MkvEntitlementServiceListener
    This interface allows a component to track the availability of the entitlement service.
    MkvEntitlementsQueryExecuteListener
    Interface used for notifying responses to entitlement requests a component has issued.
    MkvFunctionCallEvent
    This class represents a function call, stores all relevant informations, and provides methods for setting a result.
    MkvFunctionCallListener
    Interface used for notifying responses to function calls.
    MkvFunctionListener
    Interface used for notifying function call requests.
    MkvGenericAuditAvailabilityListener  
    MkvGenericAuditListener
    Interface used for notifying responses to audit calls.
    MkvGenericUserRequestListener
    Interface used for notifying OnBehalfOf registration events.
    MkvLicenseEvent
    This class represents the information relevant to a feature license request.
    MkvLicenseListener
    Interface used for notifying update events for the feature license the component has requested.
    MkvMQAckReplyListener
    Interface used for notifying events of synchronization replies sent by the subscriber of a published message queue.
    MkvMQAckRequestListener
    Interface used for notifying events of synchronization requests sent by the publisher on message queue subscriptions.
    MkvMQListener
    Interface used for notifying events on message queue.
    MkvMQSubscribeEvent
    This interface represents a Message Queue update event.
    MkvMQSubscribeListener
    Interface used for notifying events on message queue subscriptions.
    MkvMQUpdate
    This interface represents a Message Queue update event.
    MkvOnBehalfOfFeatureLicenseEvent
    This class represents the information relevant to a on behalf of feature license request.
    MkvOnBehalfOfFeatureLicenseListener
    This listener is used for on-behalf-of requests of by-feature licenses.
    MkvOnBehalfOfGenericRequestListener
    Interface used for notifying OnBehalfOf generic user authentication events.
    Application code must implement: Either the MkvOnBehalfOfGenericRequestListener.onCall(MkvGenericUserRequestResult, String, Map) or MkvOnBehalfOfGenericRequestListener.onCall(MkvGenericUserRequestResult, String) method. The MkvOnBehalfOfGenericRequestListener.onException(MkvGenericUserRequestException) method.
    MkvOnBehalfOfRegistrationListener
    Interface used for notifying OnBehalfOf registration events.
    MkvOnBehalfOfRegistrationListenerExt
    Interface used for notifying OnBehalfOf registration events.
    MkvOnBehalfOfUnRegistrationListener
    Interface used for notifying OnBehalfOf unregistration events.
    MkvPlatformListener
    Interface used for notifying platform events.
    MkvPublishListener
    Interface used for notifying publication events.
    MkvRecordListener
    Interface used for notifying data updates on records.
    MkvRecordListenerExt
    Interface used for notifying data updates on records belonging to patterns and persistent sets.
    MkvReleaseLicenseListener
    Interface used for notifying release license events.
    MkvSubscribeable
    An MkvRecord implementing this class will be automatically called in case a subscribe or unsubscribe request is remotely made against it.
    MkvSubscribeEvent  
    MkvSubscribeListener  
    MkvTimeoutListener  
    MkvTransactable
    An MkvRecord implementing this class will be automatically called in case a transaction request is made against it.
    MkvTransactionCallEvent
    This class represents a transaction request, stores all relevant informations, and provides methods for setting a result.
    MkvTransactionCallListener
    Interface used for notifying responses to transaction requests.
    MkvTransactionListener
    Interface used for notifying transaction requests.
